All application repos include this template via include pointer + 2 variables only. Vendor DevOps has zero need for Application subgroup access. (§5.1)
Define all pipeline stages in ci-templates
Stages: build · test · sast · fortify · dockerbuild · deploy-dev · create-rc-tag · deploy-{env} · deploy-hotfix-preprod-smoke · create-prod-tag · retag-image · back-merge · promote-image · deploy-prod-{env}
Auto-trigger rules per branch type
feature/bugfix push → build+test+sast+fortify (auto) | develop merge → +dockerbuild+deploy-dev (auto) | release merge → +create-rc-tag (auto) | main merge → create-prod-tag+retag+back-merge (auto)
Manual-only deploy jobs for non-DEV environments
deploy-sit / deploy-uat / deploy-int / deploy-perf / deploy-preprod-* → when: manual, only Release Manager role can trigger


